news.title: Bombay HC saves building proposal from ‘Kafkaesque’ BMC
news.para: Gufran Qureshi (38), plot owner and builder who questioned the sudden denial of permission last Dec and this Jan by the civic engineer, informed the high court that the building is constructed up to seven floors.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh government exempts DMRC & NCRTC from paying municipal taxes
news.para: A GMC official said, “We said in our plea that a central govt rule mandates municipalities across the country to levy service charges on all central and state govt buildings and installations instead of services that a municipality provides.

news.title: Ashiana Housing to invest Rs 400 crore to develop senior living project in Chennai
news.para: "The investment for Ashiana Vatsalya is primarily funded through internal resources, supplemented by a loan of 8-10%," said Ankur Gupta, joint managing director of Ashiana Housing

news.title: China's Country Garden faces liquidation petition
news.para: CHINA-PROPERTY/DEBT-COUNTRY GARDEN (UPDATE 3, PIX)UPDATE 3-Country Garden faces liquidation petition in new blow to China property sector

news.title: Essentials can be denied to defaulters under apartments act: Telangana HC
news.para: Telangana high court supported the powers of apartment associations under the Telangana Apartments Act. The court stated that apartment associations need funds for maintaining the premises and dealing with defaulters.

news.title: Delhi civic body to not extend deadline for property geo-tagging
news.para: It has also issued a public notice in this regard, explaining that there is no plan to extend the deadline of Feb 29 for taxpayers wanting to avail 10% rebate on advance payment of property tax.

news.title: IL&FS puts over 5.4 lakh sq ft GIFT City office properties on the block
news.para: Beleaguered non-banking finance company IL&FS is selling commercial properties in GIFT TWO, Gujarat’s GIFT City, as part of its debt resolution process. The properties include offices leased to Tata Consultancy Services.

news.title: Gautam Buddh Nagar administration to issue notices to builders over complaints from buyers
news.para: "It has been decided that notice would be issued to some builders, including Mahagun, Ajnara and Migsun, seeking their response over the complaints related to their housing projects," District Magistrate Manish Kumar Verma told PTI.

news.title: Bhubaneswar: Kharavela Enclave buyers protest against delay in handing over of flats
news.para: The homebuyers said the OSHB had taken up the project in 2011 with a promise to hand over completed apartments by 2014. However, 10 years have passed but the board is yet to give them the flats.

news.title: Bombay HC questions Anjuna Caisua panchayat over delay in sealing 175 illegal properties
news.para: The high court questions Anjuna-Caisua panchayat over delay in sealing 175 illegal structures in no-development and coastal regulatory zones. Panchayat faces difficulties in locating and sealing structures, requests assistance.

news.title: Chattrapati Sambhajinagar residents can avail concession upto 10% on property tax for FY25
news.para: The seven-star rating policy refers to the use of e-vehicles, segregation of garbage at source, plantation of trees, registering property against the name of female members of the family, use of solar power, implementation of rainwater harvesting and online payment of taxes.

news.title: Swedish property giants write down billions as prices crash
news.para: Heimstaden's preferential shares dropped more than 30% after Fitch cut its credit rating deeper into so-called "junk" territory and the company said it would defer hybrid bond interest payments. SBB shares fell more than 4%.

news.title: Panel to decide on civic taxes for Hi-Tech townships residents in Ghaziabad
news.para: The policy’s terms exempt the townships from house, water and sewer taxes either for seven years from the start of construction or till handover of the units, whichever is earlier. Wave City and Suncity are Hi-tech township licencees in Ghaziabad.

news.title: New home sales in USA rise by 1.5% in January 2024
news.para: New home sales increased 1.5% to a seasonally adjusted annual rate of 661,000 units last month, the Commerce Department's Census Bureau said on Monday.

news.title: Lucknow development body razes 78 slum houses to pave way to Kukrail riverfront project
news.para: The Lucknow Development Authority demolished 78 houses in Akbarnagar slums for the Kukrail riverfront development project. The operation caused emotional distress to residents, who were provided homes under the Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana. LDA vice-chairman, Indramani Tripathi, supervised the operation.

news.title: Delhi civic body passes proposal on properties 'booked' for action
news.para: An official later said "booking" refers to a property getting "booked for action" and, if an alteration or addition to an existing building is found violative of the approved building plan, the "illegal part" is marked for demolition.

news.title: Lucknow: Properties of Rohtas Project's owner worth 18.5 crore to be confiscated
news.para: A preliminary order of confiscation was passed in favour of the state under Section 14 (1) of the Uttar Pradesh Gangster and Anti-Social Activities (Prevention) Act 1986.

news.title: Home prices in Hong Kong fall by 1.6% in January 2024
news.para: Home prices in one of the world's most expensive property markets dropped 1.6% last month from the previous month, the ninth monthly fall in a row, official data showed on Tuesday, following a revised 1.5% decline in December.

news.title: Uttar Pradesh government pulls up four authorities for delaying affordable housing projects
news.para: The authorities governing Hapur-Pilkhuwa, Unnao-Shuklaganj, Kanpur and Ghaziabad have been asked to expedite work on creating the housing units which have been approved by the central sanctioning and monitoring committee (CSMC).
